import React from 'react' import PropTypes from 'prop-types' import {useQuery} from 'react-query' import {fetchNote} from '../api/index' import { Grid, Paper } from '@material-ui/core' function NoteData(props) { const {isLoading, error, data} = useQuery('note', ()=> fetchNote()) if(isLoading) return 'Loading...' if(error) return 'Fetch Error...' return (
{/* 1 2 3 4 */} {data.map(note =>( {note.title} ))}

) } export default NoteData
